title: Elon Musk’s lawsuit against OpenAI will face a jury in March
description: District Judge Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers said there was evidence suggesting OpenAI’s leaders made assurances that its original nonprofit structure would be maintained. The case will go to trial in March.
